  "title": "VT mutex safety: defer unlocks and panic recovery",
  "description": "Convert all manual VT mutex (vt.Mu) unlock sites to defer-based unlocks and add panic recovery where needed. Currently 10 sites use manual Unlock() which can deadlock the entire session if a panic occurs mid-critical-section. The recent fix in readClientInput (commit 3b69677) established the pattern — this epic applies it consistently across the codebase.",
